		  <style></style><div style="opacity:0" class="sc-bYoBSM hUVNGC __pf __pf_eU3ZcDmJ" id="__pf"><div data-pf-type="Body" class="sc-hjGZqJ fNoOP pf-1_"><div data-pf-type="Layout" class="sc-htJRVC dNJAjO pf-2_"><div data-section-id="pf-33a0" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-fmciRz bheIgq pf-3_ pf-sm-hide"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-gjNHFA gwWIgj"><div class="sc-ezbkAF A-dmbO pf-4_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gUQvok iVVDxu pf-5_"><h1 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-cTAqQK eHolsa pf-6_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jKTccl dCeBIC pf-8_">和紙布：千年工藝，穿越時空的文化價值</span></h1></div></div></div><div class="sc-ezbkAF A-dmbO pf-9_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c pf-sm-hide" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gUQvok iVVDxu pf-10_ pf-sm-hide"><div data-pf-type="Image" class="sc-jgrJph bzUUvT pf-11_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0560/7607/5157/t/25/assets/20221108-163527-1667901928926.jpg?v=1667901930" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0560/7607/5157/t/25/assets/20221108-163527-1667901928926.jpg?v=1667901930 1536w" width="1920" height="1080"/></div></div></div></div><div class="sc-ezbkAF A-dmbO pf-12_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gUQvok iVVDxu pf-13_"><p class="sc-jtXEFf jydWoQ pf-14_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jKTccl dCeBIC pf-16_">「和紙」（washi paper）是以日本極為傳統的工藝所製成的紙類，歷史已可追溯回1,500年前。<br><br>不過，由於近年快時尚 (Fast Fashion) 的發展，市場上的流行服飾需求量大，再加上人造絲製作成本相對低廉，因此和紙衣漸漸被取而代之；儘管傳統的和紙日趨退居幕後，不過又隨著文化與技藝的保存風潮，這項傳承有千年歷史的日本「和紙」再一次的回到我們的視線裡。</span></p><p class="sc-jtXEFf jydWoQ pf-17_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jKTccl dCeBIC pf-19_">甚至在2014年，日本和紙被登錄為「日本無形文化遺產」。</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-ezbkAF A-dmbO pf-20_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gUQvok iVVDxu pf-21_"></div></div></div><div class="sc-ezbkAF A-dmbO pf-22_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gUQvok iVVDxu pf-23_"><h2 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-cTAqQK eHolsa pf-24_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jKTccl dCeBIC pf-26_">日本和紙，皇室御品也是日常用紙</span></h2></div></div></div><div class="sc-ezbkAF A-dmbO pf-27_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c pf-sm-hide" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gUQvok iVVDxu pf-28_ pf-sm-hide"><div data-pf-type="Image" class="sc-jgrJph bzUUvT pf-29_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0560/7607/5157/t/25/assets/-1647940920580.png?v=1647940937" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0560/7607/5157/t/25/assets/-1647940920580.png?v=1647940937 1536w" width="832" height="512"/></div></div></div></div><div class="sc-ezbkAF A-dmbO pf-30_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gUQvok iVVDxu pf-31_"><p class="sc-jtXEFf jydWoQ pf-32_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jKTccl dCeBIC pf-34_">日本和紙又可以分為最古老的岐阜縣「本美濃紙」、島根縣的「石州半紙」，以及埼玉縣的「細川紙」。</span></p><p class="sc-jtXEFf jydWoQ pf-35_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jKTccl dCeBIC pf-37_"><b>「本美濃紙」</b>在江戸時代即是王室的御品，現代也常用以製成拉門等日式建物裡常有的設施；</span></p><p class="sc-jtXEFf jydWoQ pf-38_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jKTccl dCeBIC pf-40_"><b>「石州半紙」</b>的紙質觸感柔順但非常強靭，且能夠經得起輕微的水洗，據說在過去若發生火災，能將重要的文件檔案直接丟入水中以全其完整性。在日常的應用上，可以說是生活中最常選用的紙。</span></p><p class="sc-jtXEFf jydWoQ pf-41_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jKTccl dCeBIC pf-43_"><b>「細川紙」</b>具有紙張的光澤、高硬度，在過去也是天皇御用的邀請卡等。目前最常見的應用，則是古典飾品、日本書籍或是版畫用紙。</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-ezbkAF A-dmbO pf-44_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gUQvok iVVDxu pf-45_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-cTAqQK eHolsa pf-46_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jKTccl dCeBIC pf-48_">創新的和紙應用，推出許多經典產品</span></h3></div></div></div><div class="sc-ezbkAF A-dmbO pf-49_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c pf-sm-hide" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gUQvok iVVDxu pf-50_ pf-sm-hide"><div data-pf-type="Image" class="sc-jgrJph bzUUvT pf-51_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0560/7607/5157/t/25/assets/pexelsteonaswift6850577-1667903397506.jpg?v=1667903401" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0560/7607/5157/t/25/assets/pexelsteonaswift6850577-1667903397506.jpg?v=1667903401 1536w" width="5040" height="3360"/></div></div></div></div><div class="sc-ezbkAF A-dmbO pf-52_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gUQvok iVVDxu pf-53_"><p class="sc-jtXEFf jydWoQ pf-54_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jKTccl dCeBIC pf-56_">除了將和紙應用於各類型高端「紙類」產品，近年來更有許多創新的作法，像是將和紙製成和紙沙、紡成織，加入服飾中。例如來自溫哥華的慢時尚服飾品牌 Projext，就成功的將和紙應用到極致，推出許多經典的產品，如<a href="/products/papier-gt-white" target="_self" style="color: rgb(0, 102, 204);"><u>德訓鞋</u></a>鞋面背、<a href="/products/women-papier-tee-white" target="_self" style="color: rgb(0, 102, 204);"><u>和紙素T</u></a>、<a href="/products/papier-crew-socks-blue" target="_self"><u style="color: rgb(0, 102, 204);">和紙襪</u></a>等。</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-ezbkAF A-dmbO pf-57_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div da